---
import Layout from '../components/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Community — entity"
  description="Where to find the entity community."
>
  <section class="community">
    <div class="community__inner">
      <p class="eyebrow">Community</p>
      <h1>Find us where the code is.</h1>
      <p class="community__lede">
        entity is developed in the open. File issues, send patches, ask
        questions.
      </p>

      <div class="community__links">
        <a
          href="https://github.com/duremovich/Entity"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener noreferrer"
          class="community__card"
        >
          <h2>GitHub</h2>
          <p>Source, releases, issues, discussions.</p>
          <span class="arrow">github.com/duremovich/Entity ↗</span>
        </a>

        <a
          href="https://github.com/duremovich/Entity/issues"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener noreferrer"
          class="community__card"
        >
          <h2>Issues</h2>
          <p>Bug reports, feature requests, "is this a bug or am I holding it wrong?"</p>
          <span class="arrow">Open an issue ↗</span>
        </a>

        <a
          href="https://github.com/duremovich/Entity/discussions"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener noreferrer"
          class="community__card"
        >
          <h2>Discussions</h2>
          <p>Show-and-tell, integration help, design conversations.</p>
          <span class="arrow">Start a discussion ↗</span>
        </a>
      </div>

      <p class="community__note">
        A Discord / Matrix room will land when there's enough humans to fill
        it. Until then, GitHub is the channel.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>

<style>
  .community {
    padding: 96px 32px 64px;
  }
  .community__inner {
    max-width: 920px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }
  .community h1 {
    font-size: clamp(40px, 5vw, 64px);
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: -0.03em;
    margin: 12px 0 24px;
  }
  .community__lede {
    font-size: 18px;
    line-height: 1.6;
    color: var(--color-ink-dim);
    max-width: 56ch;
    margin: 0 0 48px;
  }
  .community__links {
    display: grid;
    gap: 16px;
  }
  .community__card {
    padding: 28px 32px;
    border-radius: 12px;
    border: 1px solid var(--color-line);
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.02);
    text-decoration: none;
    color: var(--color-ink);
    transition: border-color 0.15s ease, background 0.15s ease;
    display: block;
  }
  .community__card:hover {
    border-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.18);
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.04);
  }
  .community__card h2 {
    font-size: 20px;
    font-weight: 600;
    margin: 0 0 8px;
    letter-spacing: -0.01em;
  }
  .community__card p {
    color: var(--color-ink-dim);
    font-size: 14px;
    margin: 0 0 16px;
    line-height: 1.5;
  }
  .arrow {
    color: var(--color-accent);
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 13px;
  }
  .community__note {
    margin-top: 48px;
    color: var(--color-ink-dim);
    font-size: 14px;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }
</style>
